FBIS4-59303 "drnes092_s_94022" FBIS-NES-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 SOUTH ASIA Iran Bill Submitted on Banning Satellite Dishes Bill Submitted on Banning Satellite Dishes LD1105095994 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 0930 GMT 11 May 94 LD1105095994 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Excerpts] During today's open session of the Majles, a bill on the Islamic Republic of Iran's membership in the Sea Search and Rescue Convention was approved. [passage omitted] Also during today's open session of the Majles, a draft bill on banning private satellite receiver dishes, signed by a group of the Majles deputies, was submitted to the Majles presidium.
